# Summary
Dynamic Configuration is a feature in Amplitude SDKs (iOS 5.3.0+, Android 2.28.0+, JavaScript 8.9.0+, React Native, Unity, Flutter) that automatically selects the optimal server URL based on user location, particularly beneficial for users in Mainland China and for handling server unavailability without app updates.

